### Policy Updates API Documentation

#### Get Job Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cron/policy-updates/refresh
x-cron-secret: {{cronSecret}}

#### Trigger Policy Updates Job
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cron/policy-updates/refresh
x-cron-secret: {{cronSecret}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

